{"id":50,"date":"2021-10-07T01:10:05","date_gmt":"2021-10-07T01:10:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cagbcprod.wpengine.com\/?page_id=50"},"modified":"2023-12-22T07:55:38","modified_gmt":"2023-12-22T12:55:38","slug":"zero-carbon-building-standard-performance-resources","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/our-work\/certification\/zero-carbon-building-standard\/zero-carbon-building-standard-performance-resources\/","title":{"rendered":"Zero Carbon Building \u2013 Performance"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0px\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For building operations<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Achieving Zero Carbon Building &#8211; Performance Standard\u2122 certification means taking responsibility for all carbon emissions associated with building operations, and eliminating climate impacts. Using utility and other data sources, this certification evaluates building performance annually. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>ZCB-Performance\u2122 evaluates carbon emissions from normal building operations such as heating and cooling. It also accounts for potential refrigerant leaks and the embodied carbon of new structural and envelope materials. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/CaGBC_Zero_Carbon_Building_Standard_v2_Performance.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">The Standard <\/a>recognizes the value of renewable energy and high-quality carbon offsets while encouraging strategies that account for the ever-increasing demand on electrical grids.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/CaGBC_Zero_Carbon_Building_Standard_v2_Performance.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">The ZCB-Performance Standard<\/a> can be used by any building. Projects with combustion equipment must create a costed zero-carbon transition plan to show how equipment will be adapted over time to achieve decarbonization, often through regular equipment replacement life cycles. <\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"min-height:326px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-0 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"300\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-4682\" alt=\"Decorative image.\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_exterior_1200x300.jpg\" style=\"object-position:44% 83%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"44% 83%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_exterior_1200x300.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_exterior_1200x300-300x75.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_exterior_1200x300-1024x256.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_exterior_1200x300-768x192.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\"><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\">Understanding ZCB-Performance requirements<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Carbon<\/th><td>Zero carbon balance<\/td><td>Achieve zero carbon balance<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><\/td><td>Embodied carbon<\/td><td>Offset embodied carbon<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><\/td><td>Refrigerants<\/td><td>Offset any leaks<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><\/td><td>RECs and carbon offsets<\/td><td>Provide proof of purchase<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><\/td><td>Onsite combustion<\/td><td>Update transition plan every 5 years<\/td><\/tr><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Energy<\/th><td>Energy efficiency<\/td><td>Report EUI<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><\/td><td>Peak demand<\/td><td>Report seasonal peaks<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><\/td><td>Airtightness<\/td><td>Conduct testing if ZCB-Design certified<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"mailto:zerocarbon@cagbc.org\">Questions?&nbsp;Send us an email<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light is-style-banner-ads\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-moss-green-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"686\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-595\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-ad-become-a-member-1024x686.webp\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-ad-become-a-member-1024x686.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-ad-become-a-member-300x201.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-ad-become-a-member-768x515.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-ad-become-a-member-1536x1029.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-ad-become-a-member-2048x1372.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-cloud-white-color has-text-color has-h-9-font-size\">Register your project.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button aligncenter\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-cloud-white-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"http:\/\/leed.cagbc.org\/LEED\/Register_ZCB_Project_EN.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Start now<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-getting-started\">Getting started<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pursuing ZCB-Performance is simple. Review <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/CaGBC_Zero_Carbon_Building_Standard_v2_Performance.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">the Standard<\/a> and complete <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/ZCB-Performance_v2_Workbook.xlsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">the workbook<\/a>, providing one year of performance data. When you are ready, <a href=\"http:\/\/leed.cagbc.org\/LEED\/Register_ZCB_Project_EN.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">register online<\/a> and submit your documentation for review. For full details, review the&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ZCB_Certification_Guide-1.pdf\">ZCB Standards Certification Guide<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you receive a confirmation of certification, be sure to promote a year of operation without impact to the climate. You can refer to the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/our-work\/certification\/marketing-support\/\">Marketing Support page<\/a> to aid your promotion efforts. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-h-2-font-size\" id=\"pricing\">Pricing<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Project fees are based on a project\u2019s certification pathway and size. Fees are not refundable and may change at any time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>CAGBC Member Discounts:<\/strong>&nbsp;ZCB-Performance projects are eligible for discounts if the building owner or property management organization is a current&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/get-involved\/become-a-member\/\">CAGBC Specialist member<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/CAGBC_ZCB_pricingtable_2023_EN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">DOWNLOAD THE PRICING GUIDE<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light is-style-banner-ads\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-tree-green-background-color has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"375\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-4681\" alt=\"Decorative image. \" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_windows_1200x375.jpg\" style=\"object-position:88% 82%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"88% 82%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_windows_1200x375.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_windows_1200x375-300x94.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_windows_1200x375-1024x320.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/phenix_windows_1200x375-768x240.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-cloud-white-color has-text-color has-h-9-font-size\">Download the Standard now.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button aligncenter\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-cloud-white-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/CaGBC_Zero_Carbon_Building_Standard_v2_Performance.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">download<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color has-h-3-font-size\" id=\"resources\">Project resources&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Access the Standard and the tools projects need to achieve certification.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ZCB_Certification_Guide-1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ZCB Certification Guide<\/a> <em>applies to all versions<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-h-8-font-size\" id=\"zcb-performance-standard-v2\"><strong>ZCB-Performance Standard v2<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/CaGBC_Zero_Carbon_Building_Standard_v2_Performance.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ZCB-Performance Standard v2&nbsp;<\/a>(<em>updated June 2022)<\/em><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/portal.cagbc.org\/cagbcdocs\/zerocarbon\/v2\/ZCB-Design_v2_energy_modelling_guidelines.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Energy Modelling Guidelines<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/portal.cagbc.org\/cagbcdocs\/zerocarbon\/v2\/ZCB_v2_Life-Cycle_Cost_Calculator.xlsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Life-cycle Cost Calculator<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/ZCB-Performance_v2_Workbook.xlsx\">ZCB-Performance v2 Workbook<\/a><em> (<em>updated June 2022<\/em>)<\/em><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/portal.cagbc.org\/cagbcdocs\/zerocarbon\/v2\/ZCB_v2_Embodied_Carbon_Reporting_Template.docx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Embodied Carbon Reporting Template<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light is-style-banner-ads\" style=\"min-height:253px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-ocean-blue-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-607\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-LEED-hours-scaled.webp\" style=\"object-position:90% 69%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"90% 69%\"\/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-cloud-white-color has-text-color has-h-9-font-size\">Looking for Zero Carbon education?  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-layout-5 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-cloud-white-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/learn\/attend-an-event\/accelerating-to-zero\/\">Learn more<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n    <div class=\"is-style-section-headline \">\n        <h2 class=\"has-h-4-font-size spacing-bottom-0\" id=\"h-tech-doc\">Technical Resources<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main is-style-main--small\">\n                <a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color\" aria-describedby=\"h-tech-doc\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-insights\/technical-resources\/\">Read more<\/a>    \n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n\n\n        <div class=\"wp-custom-grid\">\n                            <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                    <div>\n                                                <h3 class=\"has-h-5-font-size\">\n                            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/technical-documents\/embodied-carbon-reporting-template-v2\/\" target=\"_self\">\n                                Embodied Carbon Reporting Template v2                            <\/a>\n                        <\/h3>\n                        <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                            o The purpose of this reporting template is to outline the information that&hellip;                        <\/div>\n                        <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                            October 7, 2021                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n                            <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                    <div>\n                                                <h3 class=\"has-h-5-font-size\">\n                            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/technical-documents\/zcb-performance-standard-v2\/\" target=\"_self\">\n                                ZCB-Performance Standard v2                            <\/a>\n                        <\/h3>\n                        <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                            The Zero Carbon Building \u2013 Performance (ZCB-Performance) Standard is a made-in-Canada framework for&hellip;                        <\/div>\n                        <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                            October 7, 2021                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n                            <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                    <div>\n                                                <h3 class=\"has-h-5-font-size\">\n                            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/technical-documents\/zcb-performance-v2-workbook\/\" target=\"_self\">\n                                ZCB-Performance v2 Workbook                            <\/a>\n                        <\/h3>\n                        <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                            This workbook must be completed and provided as part of the submission for&hellip;                        <\/div>\n                        <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                            October 7, 2021                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n                            <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                    <div>\n                                                <h3 class=\"has-h-5-font-size\">\n                            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/technical-documents\/zcb-certification-guide\/\" target=\"_self\">\n                                ZCB Certification Guide                            <\/a>\n                        <\/h3>\n                        <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                            This document provides project teams detail on the Zero Carbon Building Standards certification&hellip;                        <\/div>\n                        <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                            October 7, 2021                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n        \n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n    <div class=\"is-style-section-headline \">\n        <h2 class=\"has-h-4-font-size spacing-bottom-0\" id=\"h-news-articles-65b60a7ae7ff4\">LATEST NEWS<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main is-style-main--small\">\n                <a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color\" aria-describedby=\"h-news-articles-65b60a7ae7ff4\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-insights\/news\/                    ?thm=zero-carbon&#038;rtng=zero-carbon-building\">More                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"wp-custom-grid\">\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/expanding-the-zcb-project-information-available-online\/\">\n                                        Expanding the ZCB project information available online                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Over the comings months, CAGBC will be expanding the project information publicly available&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 10, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/survey-findings-your-thoughts-about-the-upcoming-zcb-design-standard\/\">\n                                        Survey findings: Your thoughts on the upcoming ZCB-Design Standard                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Earlier this fall we asked you for ideas to inform the ongoing evolution&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 8, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/help-inform-updates-to-zero-carbon-building-design-standard\/\">\n                                        Help inform updates to Zero Carbon Building &#8211; Design Standard                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div c